body.name: Jorkar Portable SSD Enclosure for MacBook Air/Pro 2013-2017, USB 3.2 Type C to Mac SSD, External Enclosure for Flash SSD 12+16 PIN M.2 Nvme SSD (20Gbps)
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Wednesday, February 14. Order within 17 hrs 50 mins
features: [Higher Compatibility] Jorkar USB C 3.2 SSD enclosure works well for Mac SSDs with 12+16 Pins. It comes with a M.2 NVME SSD adapter, making it also support m.2 2280 NVME SSDs. (*important*) DOES NOT support Toshiba 12+16 PIN SSDs. NOT compatible with all SATA SSDs, or third-party SSDs.

[Faster Data Transmission] 20Gbps transmission speed with USB 3.2 Gen2 interface. Save and transfer data in a second. It can also reach 20Gbps transmission speed with USB 3.2 Gen2x2 if the computer supports.

[Aluminum Alloy] Jorkar USB C 3.2 SSD enclosure is sturdy and portable, with aluminum alloy case for quicker heat dissipation. To prevent it from being disconnected from your Mac or PC. We advise you to deselect “Put hard disks to sleep when possible” both in Battery and Power Adapter.

[System Requirements] Jorkar USB C 3.2 SSD enclosure supports Windows7/8/10/11, Mac OS 10.0 or later, Linux 2.6 or later. Supports for 2013-2017 MacBook Air, for 2013-2015 2017 MacBook Pro Retina, for 2013-2014 iMac, for 2013 Mac Pro.

[Easy Installation] Just take out the PCB board from the enclosure, then fully insert SSD to card slot of the PCB board, then put PCB back into the enclosure and tighten the screws. On Windows OS, hard disk will not available on "This PC"/ "My computer", please find your drive from "Disk Management".

Please make sure your SSD is from the following models: for MacBook Air / Pro Retina 2013 2014 2015 2017 built-in SSD (NOT for MacBook 2010 2011 2012 SSDs, and NVMe protocol SSDs are not applicable.) 2. Do not move the hard drive case during use, and prevent collision with the hard drive. 3. Do not squeeze the product with external force. 4. Non-professionals should not disassemble the product or repair it. 5. When disconnecting this external hard drive, you should exit safely. If the hard drive data is accidentally lost, we are not responsible to restore any data. 6. For Mac OS PC, the hard drive should be formatted with exFAT. 7. Your internal SSD needs to be re-partitioned for normal storage and copying, otherwise it may appear unrecognizable. 8. If high transmission speed is required, please plug it into a computer equipped with USB3.0 interface.

reviews.reviewTitle: Non è del tutto conforme alle descrizioni, il promesso cavo thunderbolt 3 è fasullo.
reviews.reviewText: Funziona con le SSD apple come promesso, ma il cavo incluso non è un thunderbolt 3 manco lontanamente.Non è incluso alcun adattatore per SSD NVMe e senza di esso sono inutilizzabili. La velocità promessa è falsa.
